						<div class="row">
							<div class="span5 center">
								<h1>PHP part</h1>
								<p>It is a whole of functionnal .php files, use it if you want to create a functionnal website, or a wordpress theme. Faster to modify and implement. I advice you.<br />
								See: <a href="#php">#PHP template</a>,<a href="#new-page">#Create a new page</a>, <a href="#html">#HTML elements</a>,<a href="#design">#Customization</a>, <a href="#contact">#Contact page</a></p>
							</div>
							<div class="span5 center">
								<h1>HTML part</h1>
								<p>It is a whole of functionnal .html files, use it if you want to create a design for a use special, or a just an html website because you're not a PHP fan.<br />
								See: <a href="#html">#HTML elements</a>,<a href="#design">#Customization</a></p>
