                            <div class="span5">
                                <p><strong>Resources:</strong></p>
									<ul>
										<li>You will find here all the plugins files, icons directly download from the author's page. You will find the psd files too.
											In a word, all the files who aren't my work. See: <a href="#psd">#Photoshop</a>, <a href="#credits">#credits</a></li>
									</ul>
                                <p><strong>PHP template:</strong></p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li>Css:
                                            <ul>
                                                <li><code>style_aColor.css</code>:10 default color themes for this template, they're just style.css with the main color changed.</li>
                                                <li><code>bootsrtap.css</code>: Bootsrtap framwork.</li>
                                                <li><code>bootsrtap-responsive.css</code>: Bootsrtap framwork for mobile phones and tablets.</li>
                                                <li><code>ie8.css</code>: stylesheet for Internet Explorer 8. <a href="#compatibility">#compatibility</a></li>
                                                <li><code>ie9.css</code>: stylesheet for Internet Explorer 9. <a href="#compatibility">#compatibility</a></li>
                                                <li><code>style_responsive.css</code>: stylesheet for mobile device and tablet. <a href="#compatibility">#compatibility</a></li>
                                                <li><code>style_slider.css</code>: stylesheet for the two sliders in the home page.</li>
												<li><code>prettyPhoto.css</code>: stylesheet for Prettyphoto plugin.</li>
                                            </ul>
											See: <a href="#design">#Customization</a>
										</li>
									</ul>
                            </div><!-- end .span5 -->
                            <div class="span5 m1">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>Images: There there's this folder all the images that used to integrate the template into HTML (icons and backgrounds are also here).
										See: <a href="#psd">#Photoshop</a>, <a href="#credits">#credits</a>, <a href="#design">#Customization</a></li>
                                    <li>Js:
                                        <ul>
                                            <li><code>bootsrtap-....js</code>: Plugins used by Bootstrap (see "features -> javascript Elements"), all these javascript files are not included in the template.</li>
                                            <li><code>sequence.jquery-min.js</code>: Javascript file of the slider main style is in the file style_slider.css.</li>
											<li><code>jquery.elastislide.js</code>: Javascript file of the slider of the last projects.</li>
											<li><code>jquery.prettyPhoto.js</code>: Plugin for the "lightbox".</li>
											<li><code>main.js</code>: Javascript file of the template with the commissioning of plugins and javascript required (effect on icons, scroll to top, dropdown menu ...).</li>
											<li><code>map.js</code>: Javascript file in Google map in the contact page.</li>
											<li><code>jquery.isotope.min.js</code>: Portfolio sorter.</li>
											<li><code>prettify.js</code>: Javascript file that works with prettify.css, they allow the code documentation pages and features have a much better record.</li>
											<li><code>slides.min.jquery.js</code>: Javascript plugin used for the slider news and quotes from the home page.</li>
											<li><code>jquery.tweet.js</code>: Javascript plugin used for tweets in the widget. <a href="#social">#social</a></li>
                                        </ul>
										See: <a href="#design">#customization</a>, <a href="#credits">#credits</a>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
