					<section id="home">
						<div class="page-header">
							<h1>Home page</h1> <a href="#" class="scroller pull-right"><i class="icon-chevron-up"></i></a>
						</div>
						<p>4 kinds of home page are available in this template:</p> 
						<ul>
						<li>Home page with an unique layout: big welcome and buttons to enhance the visibility of some pages, features with icons, last projects slider.</li>
						<li>Home page with an classic layout: title, features with icons, last projects slider.</li>
						<li>Home page with complete: a slider, features with icons, "about us" box, prices, last projects slider.</li>
						<li>Other home page: a second slider, features with icons, "about us" box, prices.</li>
						</ul>
						<p>To create your own, you have to choose between them and open it.</p>
						<h3 class="m2" >Layout with the arrows and the icons</h3>
							<img src="assets/images/home.png" class="thumbnail">
							<p class="m1">It's for a home page without slider, you can welcome your visitors with a message which can not be missed ! Beautiful arrows are here to enhance the visibility your content with big buttons. All with style.</p>
						<h3 class="m2" >Features</h3>
							<p>Called "features" this area is here to present your business with your strengths. The icons are here to illustrate them, find all the icons in the folder <code>resources</code>.</p>
