                                    <pre class="prettyprint linenums">&lt;a href="http://placehold.it/720x400" rel="prettyPhoto"&gt;
	&lt;img src="http://placehold.it/360x200" alt="an image" class="thumbnail"&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;</pre>
                                    <p>Respect this structure for any photo and you will have this effect (link with <code>rel="prettyPhoto"</code> then your thumbnail).
                                    You can set many options into <code>main.js</code> (line 202).<br /> See: <a href="#credits">#credits</a></p>
