					<section id="psd">
						<div class="page-header">
							<h1>Photoshop</h1> <a href="#" class="scroller pull-right"><i class="icon-chevron-up"></i></a>
						</div>
						<p>All the photoshop files about this template are into <code>resources/psd</code>, you will find some elements who build the design and who are essential for the customization. There is no version of this template in .psd but there is a similar photoshop template in the folder <code>resources/elegance's cloud PSD</code>.</p>
						<ul>
							<li><strong>background_generator.psd</strong>: it's a small file which generates backround, put your color, choose a pattern and save it (some patterns are into <code>images/widget_patterns/</code>)</li>
							<li><strong>cadre.psd</strong>: this is the bubble that you see in, put your color and save it</li>
							<li><strong>logo.psd</strong>: this is the logo of sunrising,, if you like it, put your text and save it</li>
							<li><strong>open.psd</strong>: this is the arrow on the top right corner, put your color and save it</li>
							<li><strong>picto_map.psd</strong>: this is the logo displaying into the map in the contact page, import your logo and save it</li>
						</ul>
					</section>
