						<h3 class="m2" >Browsers</h3>
						<p>This template is ready for <strong>all the modern browsers</strong>, you will find changes with the old browsers who doesn't accept CSS3...(ie6, ie7, ie8, old opera...), if you see problems with a browser please tell it to me, so that I can correct ;) If you want to correct some problems with Internet explorer 8,9 you will find 2 stylesheets for this <code>ie8.css</code> and <code>ie9.css</code>.</p>
						
						<h3 class="m2" >Screens</h3>
						<p>This template is ready for <strong>all the devices which allow the media queries</strong>, it's tested with Ipad, Iphone and large screens, if you see problems with a device please tell it to me, so that I can correct ;) Look at <code>style_responsive.css</code>.</p>
